          "So the assignment is simple to say and hard to do. Keith, fight the drift toward harshness like it is the enemy it is. Leanne, cultivate love on purpose, do not wait to feel it. Build a household with order and warmth, because the little eyes in your home are learning what marriage and God are like from the two of you."
