            "I lift up Keith to You by name, and I confess the harsh answers, the times I raised the temperature when I could have lowered it, fired back when a gentle word would have turned the whole thing. Forgive me. I want the strength to answer softly when it is hardest.",
            "Give me the soft answer in the hot moment. Slow me down in the half-second before I fire back, and teach me the right word at the right time. Let gentleness be my reflex with him when I am poked."
